plurals.name: concurrent_access_denied_message
plurals.item: Ukufunda lencwadi ngesikhathi esifanayo kukhawulwe kumadivaysi e-%1$d noma emakhomyutheni futhi usufinyelele kulo. Vala lencwadi kokunye kokufunda, linda amaminithi ambalwa bese uzama futhi.

Uxolo, ukufunda ngesikhathi esifanayo leli bhuku kukhawulwe kwidivayisi eyodwa- noma ikhompyutha futhi usufinyelele lomkhawulo. Sicela uvale lencwadi kwabanye abafundi, linda amaminithi ambalwa bese uzama futhi.
